      {
        "id": "msg-001",
        "role": "user",
        "content": "What is AI OS?",
        "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:30:00Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "msg-002",
        "role": "assistant",
        "content": "AI OS is a local-first cognitive operating system. It gives you a personal AI agent that runs entirely on your machine — your data never leaves your device. It has identity threads, memory consolidation, feeds integration, and a subconscious processing loop that learns from your conversations over time.",
        "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:30:05Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "msg-003",
        "role": "user",
        "content": "How does the memory system work?",
        "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:31:00Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "msg-004",
        "role": "assistant",
        "content": "The memory system has three layers:\n\n1. **Short-term memory** — Recent conversation turns held in a buffer\n2. **Temporary facts** — Extracted insights awaiting your approval\n3. **Long-term memory** — Approved facts consolidated into identity threads\n\nThe subconscious loop processes conversations in the background, extracting facts and strengthening neural pathways through a potentiation system inspired by how biological memory works.",
        "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:31:08Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "msg-005",
        "role": "user",
        "content": "Can you show me what threads look like?",
        "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:32:00Z"
      },
      {
        "id": "msg-006",
        "role": "assistant",
        "content": "Sure! Navigate to the **Threads** page to see all your cognitive threads. Each thread represents a domain of self-knowledge:\n\n- **Identity** — Who you are, preferences, background\n- **Philosophy** — Your beliefs, values, worldview\n- **Reflex** — Communication patterns, tone, style\n- **Form** — Tools and capabilities\n\nEach thread has its own health score based on how many facts it contains and how recently they've been updated.",
        "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:32:12Z"
      }
    ]
  },
